name: Untitled Platformer 399
description:
The first game i have made from start to finish.

Use arrows to move.

You can't jump.

The special levels are:

1st - The first game concept i didn't want to flesh out.

2nd - A level that i think wouldn't fit the game.

This game was made for QaziJam9.

EDIT: I forgot to take out the jump code from the game which made absolutely no sense. xDDD
